Package: masonmd
Type: Package
Title: Make Sense of Nonsense-Mediated Decay
Version: 0.1.0
Description: This package is used to annotate a mutation as an NMD-elicit
    mutation or not. NMD-elicit mutations can activate the nonsense-mediated decay
    pathway and degrade mutated mRNA.
